Date: Sun, 1 Feb 2026 00:06:39 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 09/16] feat(03-02): gate settings tiers by expert mode

- Add @AppStorage("expertModeEnabled") to Settings struct
- ALWAYS VISIBLE: User, Channels, Share QR Code, Display, Ambient
  Lighting, Firmware Updates, About, App Settings, Routes, Route Recorder
- GREYED OUT: Device, Power, Network, Logs show muted style with
  "Enable Expert Mode to edit" caption, not tappable
- HIDDEN: LoRa, Security, Bluetooth, Position, Canned Messages,
  Detection Sensor, External Notification, MQTT, Range Test, PAX
  Counter, Ringtone, Serial, Store & Forward, Telemetry
- Expert mode indicator with wrench icon at top of settings list
- .onChange clears navigation state when expert mode disabled
- Module section hidden when no visible items (ambient lighting unsupported)
- Section headers use simplified names in basic mode
- Zero changes to .navigationDestination switch block
---
